# Data Structures

## UnauthorizedError (object)

+ `status` (enum, required)
  + `unauthorized`
  + `internalError`


# Resource Prototypes

## NotFound

+ Response 404 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + `status`: `not found` (string, required, fixed)

## AccessDenied

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + `status`: `error` (string, required, fixed)
        + `error`: `access_denied` (string, required, fixed) - Доступ запрещен

## UserResource (NotFound)

+ Response 200 (application/json)
    + Attributes (UnauthorizedError)

+ Response 403 (application/json)
    + Attributes
        + `status`: `permission denied` (string, required, fixed)


